text: SCIC can mean: * Directorate-General for Interpretation, abbreviated after its former French name Service Commun Interprétation-Conférences * Société Centrale Immobilière de la Caisse des dépôts, the predecessor of real-estate investment company Icade * the Supreme Council of Islamic Courts, another name for the Islamic Courts Union * State Capital Investment Corporation, a state- owned company in Vietnam
title: SCIC
